entries.arrived_at_delivery: Our transport should be here any moment...
entries.arrived_at_pickup: Your delivery target (the Seinar Systems contractor) should be here very soon...
entries.attack_notify: Enemy craft detected on attack vector.
entries.docking_complete_delivery: Ah! Many thanks to Jabba and his fine pilots. Please relay that Seinar Systems would enjoy a much deeper relationship with the Hutts...
entries.docking_complete_pickup: All right! All the spice brandy is transferred. Knock yourself out, buddy.
entries.docking_started_pickup: Hey there. Hope the Seinar Systems big-wig likes spice brandy!
entries.found_loc_d: Got an update for you... follow this waypoint. Meet up with the Seinar Systems contractor.
entries.found_loc_p: Fly to this location and meet our transport.
entries.hello_d: Greetings, smuggler. We were assured that you would have a package for us. Is this true?
entries.hello_p: Good to see you, pilot! I have your delivery ready for transfer.
entries.split_quest_alert: Next, you must take a special gift to the Seinar Systems legal counsel...
entries.title: Deliver Jabba's Gifts to Imperial VIP's
